# Environment variables for the Adaptive Learning Path app.
# Populated per-feature as we add integrations. Copy to .env.local (git-ignored) and fill in.

# --- Phase 1: Vertex AI (Gemini) ---
# GCP setup steps: see Feature 1a in docs/ROADMAP.md.
# CREDENTIALS_JSON must be the FULL service-account JSON as a SINGLE LINE
# (no real newlines — `\n` inside the private_key string is fine and required).
# Flatten a downloaded key with:  jq -c . path/to/sa.json
# Paste the resulting one-line string verbatim into .env.local and into the
# Vercel dashboard env-var field. Real newlines will break JSON.parse at boot.
GOOGLE_VERTEX_PROJECT=
GOOGLE_VERTEX_LOCATION=us-central1
GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS_JSON=

# --- Phase 1: Supabase Postgres (Prisma) ---
# Both URLs come from Supabase → Project Settings → Database → Connection string.
# DATABASE_URL is the transaction-pooler URL (port 6543) — used by app at runtime.
# DIRECT_URL is the direct connection (port 5432) — used by Prisma migrations.
# Both end with ?sslmode=require. Replace [YOUR-PASSWORD] with the project password.
DATABASE_URL=
DIRECT_URL=

# --- Phase 3: Supabase Auth (added when Phase 3 starts) ---
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=

# --- Phase 3: Stripe ---
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
